# hv_sys_reg_t

**Structure**

The type of system registers.

## Declaration

```swift
struct hv_sys_reg_t
```

## Initializers

- **init(_:)**: Creates a new system-register instance.
- **init(rawValue:)**: Creates a new system-register instance.
